{"tid":706852,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲C9 推住架車要行得咁慢","createTime":"2018-06-18T08:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T10:18:37.000Z","uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec29a9564c7af510969097a22109fbbced23cee","tid":706852,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"左=C9:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   右=我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/163723_de7462425231e52cd2c011bd0792b761.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F163723_de7462425231e52cd2c011bd0792b761.png&h=4f9ec276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話就今日去惠康買嘢<br />\n啲路又鬼死咁窄<br />\n突然有個C9推住架車行我前面行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後撞到佢個屎忽<br />\n佢即刻擰轉頭話我「你唔好咁，會撞死人架」<br />\n我心諗 屌 呢家係馬路咩 你係馬路實比人咇死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1eabb9a97bd448cc7f567a4c3ed4c20b83f057","tid":706852,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"比佢話完特登等佢行幾左步先再行<br />\n望住佢行 仲以為惠康set左安全車速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知今次又撞到佢隻腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/163925_d10ef4b04cbd610ce6c2a60af485449a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F163925_d10ef4b04cbd610ce6c2a60af485449a.png&h=0dd5116a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心諗 屌 又要比佢話啦<br />\n佢即刻擰轉頭話我 不過今次讓埋條路比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻推埋架車走 直接行去要買嘢嘅貨架<br />\n一路行一路聽到佢仲話緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef2328924727bf11e049cb102a56d7cc5ca0327","tid":706852,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:42:10.000Z","msg":"仆街惠康啲嘢愈黎愈貴 <br />\n啲路就愈黎愈窄  搞到成日塞車<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老味</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00e20d0e6391411b9940ebe42dcb740f043762a","tid":706852,"uid":42268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"撞到人兩次<br />\n有冇講對唔住啊？"},{"pid":"52d385a4eafe4cd52f253777e4250edc82aa786a","tid":706852,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b00e20d0e6391411b9940ebe42dcb740f043762a","tid":706852,"uid":42268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"撞到人兩次<br />\n有冇講對唔住啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"有！ 大大聲say sorry！"},{"pid":"b722df4a2d9786dbbb089d824d451d5e6084b8fa","tid":706852,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"自己撞鳩人仲話番人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88320d092a52aae2486d1c0c8eadbd20025de612","tid":706852,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"幾時一齊玩推車"},{"pid":"1d7103c0493b621f6ea877db05c0b60666896ef8","tid":706852,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88320d092a52aae2486d1c0c8eadbd20025de612","tid":706852,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"幾時一齊玩推車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"比賽！"}]}